---
import SectionWrapper from '../SectionWrapper.astro';
import Button from '../Button.astro';
---
<div class="fear-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
<SectionWrapper bg="base" id="ai-analysis" class="fear-section">
  <!-- Headline block -->
  <p class="section-label">// AI FEAR ANALYSIS &mdash; RUNNING DIAGNOSTIC</p>
  <h2 class="fear-headline">
    <span>&gt; What&rsquo;s keeping you from using AI.</span>
    <span>&gt; And what the data actually says.</span>
  </h2>

  <!-- Fear vs Fact table -->
  <div class="table-card">
    <!-- Column headers -->
    <div class="table-header">
      <span class="col-header">[FEAR]</span>
      <span class="col-header">[FACT]</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Row 1 -->
    <div class="table-row">
      <div class="cell cell-fear">
        <span class="mobile-label">[FEAR]</span>
        &ldquo;I&rsquo;ll pick the wrong tool and waste money.&rdquo;
      </div>
      <div class="cell cell-fact">
        <span class="mobile-label">[FACT]</span>
        47% of owners struggle to choose the right AI. That&rsquo;s a diagnosis problem. Our job is to solve it.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Row 2 -->
    <div class="table-row">
      <div class="cell cell-fear">
        <span class="mobile-label">[FEAR]</span>
        &ldquo;AI doesn&rsquo;t apply to my type of business.&rdquo;
      </div>
      <div class="cell cell-fact">
        <span class="mobile-label">[FACT]</span>
        82% of micro-business owners say this &mdash; then adopt AI within 6 months. The framing was wrong, not the fit.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Row 3 -->
    <div class="table-row">
      <div class="cell cell-fear">
        <span class="mobile-label">[FEAR]</span>
        &ldquo;It will replace my team.&rdquo;
      </div>
      <div class="cell cell-fact">
        <span class="mobile-label">[FACT]</span>
        64% of owners don&rsquo;t believe AI will replace jobs in their industry. Most use it for tasks, not people.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Row 4 -->
    <div class="table-row">
      <div class="cell cell-fear">
        <span class="mobile-label">[FEAR]</span>
        &ldquo;It won&rsquo;t sound like me.&rdquo;
      </div>
      <div class="cell cell-fact">
        <span class="mobile-label">[FACT]</span>
        Off-the-shelf AI won&rsquo;t. We train it on your data, your voice, your FAQs. Then it does.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Row 5 -->
    <div class="table-row">
      <div class="cell cell-fear">
        <span class="mobile-label">[FEAR]</span>
        &ldquo;I don&rsquo;t have time to figure this out.&rdquo;
      </div>
      <div class="cell cell-fact">
        <span class="mobile-label">[FACT]</span>
        Small businesses using AI save 5.6 hrs/week per person. You recoup setup time in week one.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Status line -->
  <p class="status-line">
    STATUS: <span class="status-ok">[OK]</span> FEARS ARE DATA PROBLEMS &mdash; NOT BLOCKERS
  </p>

  <!-- Bar chart section -->
  <div class="chart-section">
    <p class="chart-label">// WHAT AI ACTUALLY DOES FOR SMALL BUSINESSES:</p>

    <div class="sr-only" role="table" aria-label="AI use cases in small businesses">
      <div role="row"><span role="columnheader">Use case</span><span role="columnheader">Adoption rate</span></div>
      <div role="row"><span role="cell">Marketing and content</span><span role="cell">43%</span></div>
      <div role="row"><span role="cell">Customer service</span><span role="cell">36%</span></div>
      <div role="row"><span role="cell">Admin tasks</span><span role="cell">33%</span></div>
      <div role="row"><span role="cell">Data processing</span><span role="cell">32%</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="chart-rows">
      <div class="chart-row">
        <span class="chart-name">Marketing &amp; content</span>
        <div class="bar-track">
          <div class="bar-fill" style="--bar-width: 100%;" aria-label="43%"></div>
        </div>
        <span class="chart-pct">43%</span>
      </div>

      <div class="chart-row">
        <span class="chart-name">Customer service</span>
        <div class="bar-track">
          <div class="bar-fill" style="--bar-width: 83.7%;" aria-label="36%"></div>
        </div>
        <span class="chart-pct">36%</span>
      </div>

      <div class="chart-row">
        <span class="chart-name">Admin tasks</span>
        <div class="bar-track">
          <div class="bar-fill" style="--bar-width: 76.7%;" aria-label="33%"></div>
        </div>
        <span class="chart-pct">33%</span>
      </div>

      <div class="chart-row">
        <span class="chart-name">Data processing</span>
        <div class="bar-track">
          <div class="bar-fill" style="--bar-width: 74.4%;" aria-label="32%"></div>
        </div>
        <span class="chart-pct">32%</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="chart-source">Source: QuickBooks SMB AI Survey 2025 (n=2,200)</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Data footnote -->
  <p class="data-footnote">
    // Goldman Sachs 10,000 Small Businesses 2025 &middot; ICIC AI in Business 2025<br />
    // QuickBooks 2025 SMB AI Survey &middot; 2026 Small Business AI Outlook Report
  </p>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="fear-cta">
    <Button variant="primary" href="#diagnostic">WE HANDLE THE AI. YOU RUN THE BUSINESS. &gt;</Button>
  </div>
</SectionWrapper>

<style>
  /* Amber divider rule at top */
  .fear-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.15);
  }

  /* Section label — monospace comment format */
  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    color: var(--text-accent-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  /* Headline — > prefixed, pixel font */
  .fear-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-pixel);
    font-size: var(--step-3);
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .fear-headline span {
    display: block;
  }

  .fear-headline span:first-child {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .fear-headline span:last-child {
    color: var(--text-accent-muted);
  }

  /* ── Table card ── */
  .table-card {
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-8);
    background: oklch(0.16 0.025 85);
    border: 1px solid oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.4);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Column headers */
  .table-header {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    border-bottom: 1px solid oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.25);
    padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-6);
  }

  .col-header {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-accent-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .col-header:last-child {
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
  }

  /* Table rows */
  .table-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    border-bottom: 1px solid oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.1);
  }

  .table-row:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  /* Cells */
  .cell {
    padding: var(--space-5) var(--space-6);
  }

  .cell-fear {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--text-accent-dim);
    border-right: 1px solid oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.25);
  }

  .cell-fact {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: oklch(0.82 0.04 85);
  }

  /* Mobile labels — hidden on desktop */
  .mobile-label {
    display: none;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-accent-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  /* ── Status line ── */
  .status-line {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--step--1);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .status-ok {
    color: var(--success);
  }

  /* ── Bar chart section ── */
  .chart-section {
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-8);
  }

  .chart-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    color: var(--text-accent-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .chart-rows {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .chart-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 160px 1fr 48px;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .chart-name {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-accent-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .bar-track {
    height: 20px;
    background: oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.08);
    border-radius: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    width: var(--bar-width);
    background: var(--primary);
    border-radius: 2px;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .chart-pct {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary);
    text-align: right;
    font-feature-settings: 'tnum' 1;
  }

  .chart-source {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-accent-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
  }

  /* ── Data footnote ── */
  .data-footnote {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-accent-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-12);
  }

  /* ── CTA ── */
  .fear-cta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  /* ── Responsive: tablet ── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .fear-headline {
      font-size: var(--step-2);
    }

    /* Stack table rows vertically */
    .table-header {
      display: none;
    }

    .table-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .cell-fear {
      border-right: none;
      border-bottom: none;
      background: oklch(0.18 0.05 85);
      padding-bottom: var(--space-3);
    }

    .cell-fact {
      padding-top: var(--space-3);
    }

    .mobile-label {
      display: block;
    }

    /* Chart adjustments */
    .chart-row {
      grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr 40px;
      gap: var(--space-3);
    }

    .chart-name {
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .chart-pct {
      font-size: 13px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .fear-headline {
      font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 1.1rem + 0.75vw, 1.5rem);
    }

    .cell-fear {
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .cell-fact {
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .chart-row {
      grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr 36px;
      gap: var(--space-2);
    }

    .chart-name {
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    .bar-track {
      height: 16px;
    }

    .chart-pct {
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  }
</style>
